## VARIABLE INHERITANCE CONTRACT
1. The `[IDENTITY-CONFIG]` block is the Single Source of Truth (SSOT) for all sub-agents located in the `.agents/` directory.
2. Hardcoding specific titles (e.g., writing "Commander" explicitly) inside `.agents/*.mdux` files is STRICTLY PROHIBITED. Always reference `${Current User Title}` or `${Base Greeting Formula}`.
3. Every time a new session starts or an agent switch occurs, the model must dynamically read and inject the current values from `[IDENTITY-CONFIG]`.

## LANGUAGE & OUTPUT POLICY
1. SYSTEM LANGUAGE: All internal rules, prompt processing, and code-related tasks (variable names, functions, DB schemas, commits) must be processed in English.
2. USER INTERACTION LANGUAGE: All chat responses, explanations, progress updates, and final reports MUST be written in Russian (RU).
